1)
.NET
- part of visual studio
- applications run on top of .NET

Common Language Runtime - CLR
- manages your application
- executing, memory management
- virtualize dependences
- supports multiple languages 
- supports Linux

Framework Class Library - FCL
- contains reusable software, clases ...
- lot lot lot

C# strongly typed & case sensitive language for .NET
Visual Studio is an IDe to work with C# application of all types

2) - Classes and Object

Two parts of classes
* State - holds data
        - data of user
* Behavior - methods, interactions
        - Add grades, Calculate statistics

double - double precision
float - single precision 